data.description: Looking for country property, close to town on a paved road?  This great property has 4.722 acres.  3 (4th bedroom or office) bedroom 2 bath home with lots of updates.  Hall bath refurbished last week & master bedroom & bath are getting a facelift this week. Original hardwood floors in living area & 2 bedroom, tile in updated kitchen, all appliances in the kitchen stay.  1 car attached garage, Storage building, 2 car detached carport with small barn & a workshop. Fenced all around with horse pens, small fenced area for garden, chickens, etc.  Fruit trees & lot of quiet.
